                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Barlow</persName>, United States
                        marshal, to Mr. <persName type="to">Fish</persName>, Secretary of
                        State.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <dateline>
                    <placeName>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">New York</hi>
                    </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1869-07-15">
                        <hi rend="italic">July</hi> 15, 1809</date>.</dateline>
                <p rend="flushleft">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Secretary of State</hi>:</p>
                <p>Authorization received. Some two hundred persons are on Gardner’s Island. They
                    refuse to leave on the request of my officers and the cutter. They have robbed
                    the light-house keeper. I must send down a sufficient force to oblige them to
                    leave. I shall act very discreetly. If I cannot get enough marines may I ask for
                    a few troops?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>FRANCIS C. BARLOW,<lb/>
                        <hi rend="italic">United States Marshal.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
